T. 13 S., R. 2 W., sec. 17, W ½;
sec. 19, all;
sec. 20, NW ¼ and S ½;
sec. 21, S ½;
secs. 25 to 36, inclusive.
T. 14 S., R. 2 W., secs. 1 to 17, inclusive;
secs. 20 to 25, inclusive.
